# Legacy ai-task track (deprecated)

If `scripts/mcp/` or `scripts/workers/` exist, this project may be on the **legacy bootstrap path** (profile `legacy-task` or pre-v2 scaffold).

## Prefer instead (v2 / Project-1 aligned)

- **Delivery:** `scripts/okf-dispatch` — see `docs/okf-dispatch-orchestration.md`
- **Lifecycle planning:** Forge MCP launchers under `scripts/*forge*.sh`
- **MCP config:** `.cursor/mcp-forge-lifecycle.json.example` → `.cursor/mcp.json`

## When legacy paths are intentional

Only use ai-task wrappers when the operator explicitly chose profile `legacy-task` or is migrating per `docs/migration-from-legacy-bootstrap.md`.

Do not add new features on `scripts/mcp/*` or `scripts/workers/*` unless the task is explicitly legacy maintenance.

The [cursor-ai-task-mcp-server](https://github.com/nicksinx/cursor-ai-task-mcp-server-updated) is **not** part of the OKF + Forge harness validated in Project-1.
